gobblin.config.store.deploy

Interface Deployable<D extends DeploymentConfig>

  • Type Parameters:
    D - DeploymentConfig or its subclasses that has configs to deploy the store
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleHDFSConfigStore

    public interface Deployable<D extends DeploymentConfig>
    An interface to deploy and rollback ConfigStores. ConfigStores that implement Deployable can be deployed using StoreDeployer
